% TXL BOM handling plugin
% A. Malton & J.R. Cordy, April 2011

% Revised July 2020

% DO NOT EDIT THIS FILE.
% Your editor may convert it and destroy the critical characters
% in the token pattern.

% Include this file in your TXL program using the command
%    include "bom.grm"
% to ignore UTF-8 BOM headers in input files, which otherwise can 
% cause parsing problems.

tokens 
    ignore ...
	|  "﻿"
	|  "﻿"
end tokens
